title: [BUG]redis-cli command auto-completion fails
body: After installing version 7.2.4 from the source code, after specifying the startup configuration file, redis-cli used the connection test and found that it could not be started in the same way as the default. There were no prompts and automatic completion when writing the redis command. I only modified the default values of daemonize, daemonize, bind, protected-mode configurations.
